data_table.description: Sample ID, body site where sample was obtained, analyte type, tumor status, histological type of sample, primary tumor or metastasis, and sequencing center of participants with pediatric rhabdomyosarcoma and involved in the "Genomic sequencing of Pediatric Rhabdomyosarcoma" project.

variable.name: BODY_SITE
variable.description: Body site where sample was collected

variable.name: HISTOLOGICAL_TYPE
variable.description: Cell or tissue type or subtype of sample

variable.name: SEQUENCING_CENTER
variable.description: Name of the center which conducted sequencing [NCI, BROAD]
